Text: Liked the story, liked the concept, some of the actors could use some acting classes, but it was definitely worth my time to watch it.  I'm looking forward to the next episode!
Independent film. Bullshit Global warming propaganda. Watched it, don't bother.

Well, the backdrop is that global warming is going to kill us in a generation, so... but the main story is about something strange.

Official website: http://www.l5-series.com/
You can get the torrent there (through the vodo.net link, 2 qualities, HD and SD).

There are 2 more torrents here on TPB, but under Other>Other, the VODO ones, both qualities.
About time there is a new scifi series.  Miss the old days of Caprica, Battlestar Gallactica and Stargate.
